caption: Excellent food, amazing bread fresh out of the oven, I was in a hurry to catch my bus and the customer service was great, very friendly workers! Thank you!

Bread=excellence.  Omg I am a bread lover and this bread is amazing.  The sandwich is fantastic.  Veggies are cold, crisp and fresh.  Meat & cheese are just the right amount.  This is a really good sandwich!
